  Locus:
    Page: 277
    Verse: 12
Tags:
  - If you have a long face and a chip
---
Spirit is never somber. Weeping with the afflicted does not help. It may
create a point of contact, but it does not bring a remedy. Joy is the
antidote for sorrow.
